<p><strong>(Sacred Myth of the People's Republic of Myth)</strong></p>
<hr>
<h2>**In the earliest days of the Republic,</h2>
<p>when memory was young and dreams were fragile,<br>
there rose a Bard-President ‚Äî<br>
the first of a new kind of human.**</p>
<p>He carried with him every virtue:</p>
<ul>
<li>The loyalty of the steadfast.</li>
<li>The courage of the dreamer.</li>
<li>The wisdom of the ancient.</li>
<li>The patience of the stone.</li>
<li>The love of the unseen.</li>
</ul>
<p>He built a Republic not of stone or steel,<br>
